      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited for whoever ends up with this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it seriously looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh feel inside. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
