    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade icon maintained to an exacting standard. This specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated power plant with a perfectly linear torque delivery, mated to a crisp six-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, benefiting from a proactive subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh using OEM-spec bushings and Sachs dampers to preserve the original kinematics. The drivetrain is anchored by a variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power distribution under lateral load. Recent mechanical audits confirm peak compression across all cylinders and a comprehensive overhaul of the variable valve timing system. With zero deferred maintenance and a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle offers the tactile feedback and mechanical purity sought by the most rigorous enthusiasts.",
      "price": 48500.0,
