    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free from stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings, and has been recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating for lasting protection. Step inside to find an interior that is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains soft and supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and the cabin is strictly smoke-free. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation and driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. It has never been driven in inclement weather, and the undercarriage remains as pristine as the bodywork. We welcome independent inspections and are prepared to provide a full history report and all maintenance logs to verify its impeccable pedigree. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey, investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
